-2 for the uploader

Actually, this is the uncut (i.e. not Directors Cut) version of the film, and as such runs 1 hour 47 minutes. The Directors Cut version removes 10 minutes.  
Okay film, not bad, but a bit on the B-movie/cheesy side. About what you would expect from a "straight to video" release, which is basically what this was. Worth a watch if only for the unusual steampunk-esque world.
